name: Queue

aliases.name: Queue
aliases.comment: The type alias for a queue
aliases.type: { enq : List a, deq : List a }

values.name: deq
values.comment:
Pulls data out of a queue

    Queue.deq q
values.type: Queue.Queue a -> ( Maybe.Maybe a, Queue.Queue a )

values.name: enq
values.comment:
Adds a data to the queue

    Queue.enq 5 q

values.name: new
values.comment:
Creates an new empty queue

    q = Queue.new

values.name: toList
values.comment:
Converts a queue to a list, (not very fast)

    Queue.toList q
